title: Ore ga Suki nano wa Imouto dakedo Imouto ja Nai
synopsis: Aspiring light novel author Yuu Nagami regularly enters writing competitions but has yet to win a single one. Despite his recurring failures, he remains steadfast in his resolve to become a better writer.
